    "However, one of the aims of CS education is to make computing systems appear not to be magic by explaining (some of) their underlying mechanisms.",
    "Only an \"undercurrent\" dealt with teaching how AI works to K-12 students (education to AI).",
    "Since the 1970s, this research followed the AI topics that were \"hot\" in the different decades, focusing, for example, on robots navigating the environment, naturallanguage processing, and expert systems.",
